Simran!  Romi!  Shekhar!

00:27:31.760 --> 00:27:32.760
Membantu!

00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:34.240
Membantu!  - Nyonya Shergill?

00:27:34.320 --> 00:27:35.320
Omong kosong!

00:27:35.920 --> 00:27:37.120
Simran.  - Saudara laki-laki.

