'Jadi, Drishti
dengan mata ketiga..'

00:42:00.480 --> 00:42:02.080 line:20%
'Temui Drishti yang lain.'

00:42:03.240 --> 00:42:04.600 line:20%
'Datang sekarang..'

00:42:04.720 --> 00:42:06.280 line:20%
'Setidaknya,
perkenalkan dirimu.'

00:42:06.360 --> 00:42:09.480 line:20%
'Saling menyapa.. Ayo.'

00:42:10.280 --> 00:42:12.480 line:20%
'Drishti di sini untuk
menemui Drishti.'

00:42:13.560 --> 00:42:15.000 line:20%
'TIDAK..'

00:42:15.720 --> 00:42:17.720 line:20%
'Drishti dengan mata
ketiga ada di sini.'